### ğŸ’° Cost Analysis (3 Users, 1 Year)

```
Odoo Online:
â”œâ”€â”€ Monthly: $24.90 Ã— 3 users = $74.70
â”œâ”€â”€ Annual: $896.40
â”œâ”€â”€ Hidden costs: None
â””â”€â”€ Total Year 1: ~$900

VPS Self-Hosted:
â”œâ”€â”€ VPS (DigitalOcean/Linode): $20/month = $240/year
â”œâ”€â”€ Domain: $12/year
â”œâ”€â”€ SSL: Free (Let's Encrypt)
â”œâ”€â”€ Setup Time: 4-8 hours (one-time)
â”œâ”€â”€ Maintenance: ~2-4 hours/month
â””â”€â”€ Total Year 1: ~$250 + time investment

Break-even: VPS saves ~$650/year
BUT requires DevOps skills + ongoing maintenance time
```

