## Migration Path (Future Growth)

### Phase 1: á€…á€á€„á€ºá€á€»á€­á€”á€º (á€œá€€á€ºá€›á€¾á€­)
- Odoo Online (SaaS)
- Basic accounting functionality
- Laravel API integration
- Single user/limited users

### Phase 2: Scale á€œá€¯á€•á€ºá€á€»á€­á€”á€º
**Option A: Odoo.sh á€á€½á€„á€º Upgrade**
- More users á€œá€­á€¯á€¡á€•á€ºá€œá€¬á€á€±á€¬á€¡á€á€«
- Custom modules develop á€œá€¯á€•á€ºá€á€»á€„á€ºá€á€±á€¬á€¡á€á€«
- Git integration á€œá€­á€¯á€¡á€•á€ºá€á€±á€¬á€¡á€á€«

**Option B: VPS Migration**
- Long-term cost savings
- Full control needed
- Multiple modules usage
- Heavy customization required

### Phase 3: Enterprise Scale
- Multiple companies support
- Advanced integrations (CRM, Inventory, etc.)
- Custom module development
- Dedicated infrastructure

