## Security Checklist

### Odoo Online
- âœ“ Enable 2FA for all users
- âœ“ Use strong passwords
- âœ“ Regularly review user permissions
- âœ“ Monitor API usage
- âœ“ Keep API keys secure

### VPS Deployment
- âœ“ Enable UFW firewall
- âœ“ Install fail2ban
- âœ“ Use SSH keys (disable password auth)
- âœ“ Enable SSL/TLS
- âœ“ Regular security updates
- âœ“ Strong database passwords
- âœ“ Restrict Odoo admin password
- âœ“ Regular backups (offsite)
- âœ“ Monitor access logs
- âœ“ Implement IP whitelisting (if possible)

